summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from U. R. Niesz and Ada B. Niesz his wife, to the City of Seattle, executed on September 17, 1912, for Lot Nine (9) and the north Five (5) feet of Lot Ten (10), Block Thirty-three (33), and Lots Seven (7), Eight (8), Nine (9), and the North Five (5) feet of Lot Ten (10), Block Thirty-four (34), The Boston Company's Plat of West Seattle, and extending Avalon Way across said tract.
